Frequently Asked Questions
Who can use StatWellMD’s weight loss program?
Adults who want safe, clinically guided weight loss using modern medication and digital support.
How does StatWellMD work?
Simply fill out a quick online form. A licensed provider reviews your case and sends your prescription to your preferred pharmacy.
Can I get GLP-1 medication through StatWellMD?
Yes — eligible patients can receive compounded GLP-1 treatments or Zepbound after clinical review.
How soon will I see results?
Most patients start noticing visible progress within 4–6 weeks of consistent use.
Is this treatment safe?
All prescriptions are reviewed and monitored by licensed U.S. clinicians to ensure safety and effectiveness.

